reviewText: That was a beautiful masterpiece production.  Great DVD even if you only understand English and even if you're not Christian, you will like the music. Fantastic!!!

What an awesome DVD .He does an awesome job relaying his love for the lord in all his songs to his audience he says everything I'm not able to but want to you can feel the anointing just hearing the songs it feels like your there at his concerts. What an anointed man of God. May he reach more people through his songs for the Lord.
tremendo concierto el mejor de Jesus Adrian Romero no me canso de verlo una y otra vez pone tus emociones y sentimientos a mil una conexion directa con Dios.

Jess Adrin Romero, is one of my favorite Latin Christian singers. The concert was what I expected & more. The most beautiful Christian songs that awake the soul. They make you want to sing along with Jess A. Romero in worship and praise God. May God continue to bless him.

Jesus Adrian Romero es, hoy por hoy, el mejor escritor de canciones cristianas de esta poca. Todos los temas tienen mensajes que llegan al alma, y la interpretacion es consecuente. La Orquesta filarmonica le da un aire de sofisticacion y a la vez sencillez nunca antes vista en la musica de este genero. Felicitaciones a la produccion y que sigan los exitos!
exelente disco para todos  los que disfrutan de la vida con cristo nuestro seor .dj ohzono
